331
00:24:37,960 --> 00:24:39,600
Eles cortam o bolo.

332
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,000
Sorvete.

333
00:24:46,120 --> 00:24:48,480
"Taif". É um dos garotos.

334
00:24:48,480 --> 00:24:50,880
O irmão dela se chama Taif.

335
00:24:51,040 --> 00:24:52,560
- Taif?
- Sim.

336
00:24:52,680 --> 00:24:55,200
O menino que vimos na foto.

337
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:59,440
Ela pretende viver uns cem anos,

338
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:00,960
